name: #7. RYAN "BOT EATER" RIZZOLI
description:
Has a particular distaste for the wrong kind of robot. If you want something fixed, and by that we mean broken, Mr. Rizzoli is your man.

"What belongs to you but is used mostly by others?" 
"What has a neck but no head?" 
"What fills up a room but takes up no space?" 

'r' toggles auto-rotate. 'l' toggles cursor following.
